snippet.title: Wizardry School: Escape Room - Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1991980/Wizardry_School_Escape_Room/

The School Headmaster needs your help to recover the Philosopher's Stone. In this escape room you will have to explore your wizardry school, solve puzzles, learn new spells and put your magical skills to the test. Will you save the school?
